title: Element Make It Count - Germany 2015
description:
Congrats to TABO LOECHELT who won the MAKE IT COUNT contest in Bremen, Germany !
Tabo won a spot in the European Finals that will take place in Spain and a chance to win a trip to California to compete for Element sponsorship at Nyjah's park!
